descriptionHTML:
How it feels, when your cat is living inside your watch? ☕

Well, you can see it by downloading Tricky Cat Watch Face.
The cat is trying to balance on the minute arrow, and sometimes it's so funny. You will like it.

Features:
•  Watchface for Android Wear Device. Compatible with most popular smartwatches: Moto 360, LG G Watch R, LG G Watch, Sony Smartwatch 3, Samsung Gear Live, Asus ZenWatch, LG Watch Urbane and many others.
•  Support both round and square displays
•  Cat animated in both, ambient and color mode

That is the only watch face that have cat inside.

Your app experience is important to us. If you find any problems or issues, email vitaminlabs.help@gmail.com for a direct response and please, support the application with five stars to help spread it across the world.

Meow, meu, meow...
comments: Cute. And it works fine. I would give five stars if there was an option to display the date though.
